{
  "page": "Moreo Tumitis",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\"><img alt=\"Tyrosh.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/50px-Tyrosh.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/75px-Tyrosh.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/100px-Tyrosh.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Captain</span><br />Moreo Tumitis</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\"><img alt=\"Tyrosh.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/50px-Tyrosh.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/75px-Tyrosh.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/100px-Tyrosh.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Alexandre_Dainche_Moreo_Tumitis.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Alexandre Dainche Moreo Tumitis.jpg\" src=\"/images/7/77/Alexandre_Dainche_Moreo_Tumitis.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"194\" /></a><div>by Alexandre Dainche. © Fantasy Flight Games</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nCaptain of <i><a href=\"/index.php/Storm_Dancer\" title=\"Storm Dancer\">Storm Dancer</a></i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyroshi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nor before <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_268_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">268&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Moreo Tumitis</b> is captain of the ship <i><a href=\"/index.php/Storm_Dancer\" title=\"Storm Dancer\">Storm Dancer</a></i>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appareance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appareance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appareance_and_Character\">Appareance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moreo_Tumitis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appareance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Moreo has a forked green beard. Hailing from <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a>, he can speak the <a href=\"/index.php/Common_Tongue\" title=\"Common Tongue\">Common Tongue</a> fluently.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moreo_Tumitis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Moreo has sailed the <a href=\"/index.php/Narrow_sea\" title=\"Narrow sea\">narrow sea</a> for roughly thirty years, first as oarman, then as quartermaster, and now as captain of trading galleys. <i><a href=\"/index.php/Storm_Dancer\" title=\"Storm Dancer\">Storm Dancer</a></i> is his fourth ship and the fastest of them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moreo_Tumitis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moreo_Tumitis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Moreo is at <a href=\"/index.php/White_Harbor\" title=\"White Harbor\">White Harbor</a> with his ship when <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Cassel\" title=\"Rodrik Cassel\">Rodrik Cassel</a> arrive to take passage south to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. They book passage on <i><a href=\"/index.php/Storm_Dancer\" title=\"Storm Dancer\">Storm Dancer</a></i>, which is the swiftest available in the harbor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When the galley arrives at the capital, Moreo suggests the travelers stay at an <a href=\"/index.php/Old_inn_on_Eel_Alley\" title=\"Old inn on Eel Alley\">old inn on Eel Alley</a>. Catelyn rewards each of his oarmen with a <a href=\"/index.php/Currency\" title=\"Currency\">silver stag</a>. Moreo offers to hold onto his crew's silver until they return to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a>, but Catelyn insists on personally paying each oarman.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"City Watch of King&#39;s Landing\">City Watch of King's Landing</a> arrive at the old inn with orders to escort Catelyn to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>; Catelyn assumes that Moreo sold her whereabouts for a price. When Catelyn asks Petyr how he knew she was in the city, her childhood friend replies that Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a> knows all.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moreo_Tumitis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><i>Storm Dancer</i> is in White Harbor when Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a> arrives on <i><a href=\"/index.php/Merry_Midwife\" title=\"Merry Midwife\">Merry Midwife</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moreo_Tumitis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Moreo</b>: My good friend. It is so fine to see you looking better.<br />\n<b>Rodrik</b>: Yes. I haven't wanted to die for almost two days now.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Moreo and <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Cassel\" title=\"Rodrik Cassel\">Rodrik Cassel</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Moreo</b>: Yet first, if I may be so bold, there is the matter of the second half of the payment we agreed upon. And of course the extra <a href=\"/index.php/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a> you were so kind as to promise. Sixty <a href=\"/index.php/Currency\" title=\"Currency\">stags</a>, I believe it was.<br />\n</p><p><b>Catelyn</b>: For the oarmen.<br />\n<b>Moreo</b>: Oh, of a certainty. Though perhaps I should hold it for them until we return to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a>. For the sake of their wives and children. If you give them the silver <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">here</a>, my lady, they will <a href=\"/index.php/Dice\" title=\"Dice\">dice</a> it away or spend it all for <a href=\"/index.php/Brothel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brothel\">a night's pleasure</a>.<br />\n<b>Rodrik</b>: There are worse things to spend money on. Winter is coming.<br />\n<b>Catelyn</b>: A man must make his own choices. They earned the silver. How they spend it is no concern of mine.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Moreo</b>: As you say, my lady.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Moreo, <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Cassel\" title=\"Rodrik Cassel\">Rodrik Cassel</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyroshi</a> knew who they were and where they were, damn him. She hoped he'd gotten a good price for the information.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moreo_Tumitis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued2)#Moreo_Tumitis\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued2)\">Moreo Tumitis</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\">2.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\">2.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\">2.6</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-7\">2.7</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_18\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 18\">Chapter 18</a>, Catelyn IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Davos II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403174615\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.124 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.432 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 922/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10907/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 10858/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2267/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3120/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.280/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.54 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  409.330      1 -total\n 95.82%  392.221      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.41%  390.536      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.28%   42.094     12 Template:Infobox_